{"word":"G2431 - ἱλαρός - hilarós - hil-ar-os' - Cheerful","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἱλαρός</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hilarós</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hil-ar-os'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Cheerful</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"உற்சாகமான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"cheerful, joyous, prompt to do anything"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From the same as <a href=\"#/G2436 - ἵλεως - híleōs - hil'-eh-oce/2436\">G2436</a>; <i>propitious</i> or <i>merry</i> (&ldquo;hilarious&rdquo;), that is, <i>prompt</i> or <i>willing:</i> - cheerful.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2431/2431\">G2431</a>, <a href=\"#/G2432/2432\">G2432</a>"}]}